text: Aadu Must Aadu is an Estonian male given name. Its variant is Ado. All these names are variants of the names Adam and Adolf. Some of the known bearers of this name are: *Aadu Birk or Ado Birk (1883–1942), Estonian politician and Prime Minister of Estonia * (1910–1989), Estonian writer * (1939–2006), Estonian businessman * (born 1951), Estonian historian and politician Aadu
title: Aadu (name)
